Rule 4     select_list -> STAR
Rule 5     select_list -> column_list
Rule 6     column_list -> ID
Rule 7     column_list -> column_list COMMA ID
Rule 8     condition -> ID EQUAL value
Rule 9     value -> NUMBER
Rule 10    value -> STRING

